{"tid":619973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強國怪風】全球最大6噸秦始皇銅像竟吹塌 網民：暗示「帝制」倒台？","createTime":"2018-04-07T07:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T05:44:22.000Z","uid":35468,"like":75,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"c37d996f2e6043dd973c5a03955ab12f50149631","tid":619973,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:12:35.000Z","msg":"2018-04-07 09:55:48 HKT\t<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180407&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58043424\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180407%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58043424&d=lRYOs8fSOO9nUw%2FeNYAX1rIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=a69f61e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180407%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58043424&h=53f2f4db\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180407&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58043424</a><br />\n山東省濱州市一座高19米、重6噸，號稱全球最大的秦始皇銅像，昨日在強風下被吹倒，無人受傷。這雖然是一宗普通的事故，但內地網民即時聯想到解除任期限制、形同稱帝的習近平，他們留言暗諷：「專制帝王抵抗不住春風！」「老天爺也看不下去了！」「暗示&hellip;&hellip;倒台！」「凶兆，某人怕不怕？」「獨裁者逆天而立，倒是天意！」<br />\n<br />\n內地媒體報道，濱州昨日狂風大作，當地氣象局發出大風黃色預警，這座於2005年9月建成的秦始皇銅像，「在狂風助力下，騰空而起，飛出數十米，被吹倒在地面目全非，銅製的冕旒也散落了一地」。報道又稱，由於銅像實在太大，「當地工作人員都束手無策」，銅像臉部嚴重破壞，被完全壓扁，最後工作人員用拖車將殘骸拖走。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民把消滅六國、高度集權、焚書坑儒的秦始皇，聯想到剛剛登基的「習帝」，說這銅像被吹倒「好像寓意不太好」，更有網民稱這是「凶兆」，「老天爺也看不下去了」，更多網民稱事件後，「趕緊報告『黃』上」，「省長的位子懸了」。網民的意件實在太過激烈，社交媒體上很多都已經不能再留言評論。<br />\n<br />\n網民意見：<br />\n<br />\n希雅士：暗示集權者會&hellip;&hellip;倒？<br />\n<br />\nsaltwater_river：暗示皇權倒台！<br />\n<br />\nQwerty_122：哈哈，凶兆。某人怕不怕？<br />\n<br />\n凜冬將至醉意漸濃：暗示帝制被吹翻！<br />\n<br />\n初學者的未知數：多行不義必自斃！<br />\n<br />\n一個跳大神兒的：專制帝王抵抗不住春風！<br />\n<br />\nsina的浪：老天爺也看不下去了！<br />\n<br />\n娜金拉措就是sunny：好像寓意不太好&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n桅儂：同治的都倒了，磚制的能不倒嗎？<br />\n<br />\n舞毛苟的靈道：糾結，我該說好還是不好呢？請指示&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\naaappp65：省長的位子懸了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n雲裳花容露華濃：趕緊報告黃上！<br />\n<br />\n新浪微博"},{"pid":"c520b64003c7c7ba361d5a4a259daa160633e1a0","tid":619973,"uid":41821,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:14:40.000Z","msg":"反了反了"},{"pid":"ef2090ba01a813e8eadf7a832977941394a1a33f","tid":619973,"uid":22422,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:16:30.000Z","msg":"秦始皇都變埋敏感詞囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e8cbf15bf90e175206ab5fe9268d7f46097ab3","tid":619973,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4513d4261f3e5876b10ebf41a607ff54c369aa","tid":619973,"uid":204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:18:48.000Z","msg":"一定有古怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1589fa49341cd259b252435a04cf4d804b3671b","tid":619973,"uid":19713,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:28:05.000Z","msg":"濱州昨日狂風大作"},{"pid":"ff96a66dc46b49067d63f920c5c6a7aa2331d355","tid":619973,"uid":42435,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:31:42.000Z","msg":"大地在我脚下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b559bb2b2702f6c51ac37662d2c0433bd99d7bcf","tid":619973,"uid":26675,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:34:07.000Z","msg":"告泰始皇顛覆國家政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7992949e6d378e5d2d59c0ff9e153bd0457cc465","tid":619973,"uid":131323,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:35:40.000Z","msg":"會唔會係得600kg<img src=\"/assets/fa